metadata.name: Assault #1
metadata.description:
First assault.

The two superheroes met at a remote beach in the country of Spain for the first assault.

After a long exchange of blows and threats, Superman's super strength and flight could not overcome Batman's intellect.

Superman ended up buried, and officially Batman is the winner of the first round.

Unique 1/1 Artwork.
2048 x 1365 px
